	<legis-body>
 <section id="idDDB3D8697DE948E19C57E2AF08F71383" section-type="section-one"><enum>1.</enum><header>Short title</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>Stop Trafficking in Fentanyl Act of 2015</short-title></quote>.</text> </section><section id="id532F93A14423453AA258970B94CB8608" section-type="subsequent-section"><enum>2.</enum><header>Enhanced penalties</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">Section 401(b)(1) of the Controlled Substances Act (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/21/841">21 U.S.C. 841(b)(1)</external-xref>) is amended—</text>
 <paragraph id="id7D6584AB5579480B939292F61DF3D6B3"><enum>(1)</enum><text>in subparagraph (A)(vi)—</text> <subparagraph id="id29462A2DC6C540A58DDA12DC6EFF1120"><enum>(A)</enum><text>by striking <quote>400 grams</quote> and inserting <quote>20 grams</quote>; and</text>
 </subparagraph><subparagraph id="id3AC209D6BF064D2FA9B4642A84B57E9B"><enum>(B)</enum><text>by striking <quote>100 grams</quote> and inserting <quote>5 grams</quote>; and</text> </subparagraph></paragraph><paragraph id="idA40002DE137843C797A39F59F47862E8"><enum>(2)</enum><text>in subparagraph (B)(vi)—</text>
 <subparagraph id="id44CEA6BADA244346A15DB37C0F4B9D31"><enum>(A)</enum><text>by striking <quote>40 grams</quote> and inserting <quote>2 grams</quote>; and</text> </subparagraph><subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idCE005D13AA1745CD8C5CBE1BE28813DD"><enum>(B)</enum><text>by striking <quote>10 grams</quote> and inserting <quote>0.5 grams</quote>.</text>
				</subparagraph></paragraph></section></legis-body>
